<section sectnbr = "9K">
<servcat sctnbr = "09" scnbr = "11">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ASLAP70A9B06010" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Demontáž a montáž vonkajšieho plechu stĺpika A, výstuhy pántov predných dverí a panel na strane prístrojovej dosky
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Nižšie uvedený obrázok zobrazuje podmienky odstraňovania nasledovných častí.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Predný blatník 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9A06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Časť zámky kapoty, časť podpory lampy a podpora lampy 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B06001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vonkajší prvok bočného krytu 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Predný panel prístrojovej dosky s predným panelom horného krytu 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B06006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0040.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.208mm" ver = "01" gw = "227" gh = "143"/>
</figure>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A9B06010001">
<title>
Všeobecné poznámky
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Spôsob zvárania a počet bodov zvaru je ten istý na oboch stranách. Tieto pokyny na opravu zobrazujú postup pre ľavú stranu.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Časť vyplnená penovým materiálom je zahrnutá v častiach tejto opravy. Preto sa obráťte na 
<intxref refid = "ASLAP70A9B06026">Oprava oblasti naplnenia penovým materiálom</intxref>
, kde nájdete bezpečnostné opatrenia a postup opravy.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Rozmery zobrazené na obrázku sú referenčné hodnoty pri rezaní náhradnej časti umiestnenej na hornej strane existujúcej časti. Určite najvhodnejšiu čiaru rezu (alebo spoja) s ohľadom na obe veľkosti náhradnej časti a podmienok existujúcej časti.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A9B06010002">
<title>
Demontáž
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Označte v zobrazenej polohe a odrežte vonakjší plech stĺpika A.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvŕtajte body zvarov.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ohnite otvorený kovový jazýček (šípka) a vyberte vonkajší plech stĺpika A.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0068V.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "210.274mm" ver = "06" gw = "497" gh = "580"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvŕtajte body zvarov a vyberte výstuhu pántov predných dverí, zarážku pántov dverí a hornú výstuhu predných dverí.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0041.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "153.828mm" ver = "07" gw = "406" gh = "420"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.878in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 :
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pri ohreve v okolí penového materiálu odmontujte penový materiál, uistite sa, že vyššie uvedená teplota nedosahuje 170 &#176;C (338 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvŕtajte body zvarov a odmontujte výstuhu strany prístrojovej dosky.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0042.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "146.437mm" ver = "01" gw = "486" gh = "399"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvŕtajte body zvarov.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odskrutkujte 3 skrutky a vyberte panel prístrojovej dosky.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0069.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "140.497mm" ver = "06" gw = "491" gh = "382"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ak je to potrebné, vybrúste body zvaru pomocou brúsky.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pri ohreve v okolí tesnenia odmontujte tesnenie karosérie, uistite sa, že vyššie uvedená teplota nedosahuje 170 &#176;C (338 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A9B06010003">
<title>
Montáž
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Pred zváraním skontrolujte polohu inštalácie a stav inštalačnej časti (častí). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B04006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B04007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
V oprave pokračujte berúc do úvahy inštaláciu častí, ktoré majú vplyv na vzhľad. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B04003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte prístrojovú dosku.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte odporové bodové zváranie a dierové zváranie.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Utiahnite 3 skrutky na predpísaný uťahovací moment.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0070.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "143.545mm" ver = "02" gw = "491" gh = "390"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.789in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MATORQUE-A" width = "8.011mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 :
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
10 N&#183;m (1,0 kgf-m, 7,5 lbf-ft)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte výstuhu prístrojovej dosky.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte odporové bodové zváranie a dierové zváranie.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0044.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "146.437mm" ver = "02" gw = "486" gh = "399"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte zarážku pántov dverí a hornú výstuhu pántov predných dverí.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte odporové bodové zváranie alebo dierové zváranie.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0045.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "121.213mm" ver = "04" gw = "204" gh = "327"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Opravte penový materiál. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A9B06026"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0046.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "162.701mm" ver = "03" gw = "485" gh = "445"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "8" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.745in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.730in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "1.215in"/>
<colspec colnum = "7" colname = "7" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "8" colname = "8" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Penová hmota
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Výstuha pántov predných dverí
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Bočný plech kapoty
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "7" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "8" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ochranný plech
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte výstuhu pántov predných dverí.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte dierové zváranie.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0047.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "153.828mm" ver = "05" gw = "406" gh = "420"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Na karosériu vozidla namontujte nový vonkajší plech stĺpika A a odrežte v naukladaných podmienkach.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte vonkajší plech stĺpika A.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte odporové bodové zváranie a dierové zváranie.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vykonajte priebežný zvar.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Na zadnú stranu časti s priebežným zvarom aplikujte antikorozívny vosk.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ohnite kovový jazýček (šípka) vonkajšieho plechu stĺpika A.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0071V.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "231.685mm" ver = "06" gw = "497" gh = "640"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.706in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 :
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Veďte odporové bodové zváranie ako cez trojpanelovú hrúbku.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
